  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to test whether platelet transfusion or fibrinogen concentrate is the most&#xD;
      effective treatment of intraoperative bleeding, when performing open heart surgery with&#xD;
      cardiopulmonary bypass on children with congenital heart defects.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
